OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and overnight.
OL,7,FSome prolonged spells of evening
OL,8,Fsunshine leading to clear spells
OL,9,Fovernight. Fresh northerly evening
OL,10,Fwinds will ease and back northwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry and bright first thing but
OL,13,Fincreasingly clouding over from the
OL,14,Fwest through the morning with a few
OL,15,Foutbreaks of light rain through the
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening, mainly for
OL,17,FOrkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
