OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fand Wednesday mainly dry and cloudy
OL,7,Fbut with some sunny intervals, most
OL,8,Flikely for Shetland. Generally
OL,9,Fcloudier on Tuesday with some patchy
OL,10,Fdrizzle.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
